      • putAll

        public TensorBuilder<V> putAll(Tensor<V> tensor)
        Description copied from interface: TensorBuilder
        Puts all the values of the given tensor into the new tensor, at the given position. The positions in the new tensor will be the merged positions of the original coordinates in the tensor with the given target position. Therefore, the given position is not allowed to have a dimensions overlap with the positions in the original tensor.
        Specified by:
        putAll in interface TensorBuilder<V>
        Parameters:
        tensor - the tensor, whose values to add to the tensor under construction
